WEBVTT

00:02.503 --> 00:04.635
WHAT´S ALL THIS STUFF?

00:04.635 --> 00:07.038
I´M GIVING IT TO THE SHELTER
 FOR THANKSGIVING.

00:07.038 --> 00:09.080
I DON´T MIND YOU HELPING
 THE HOMELESS,

00:09.080 --> 00:10.381
BUT DON´T GIVE THEM
 ALL MY GOOD STUFF.

00:10.381 --> 00:13.414
HOMESTYLE SOUPS
 WILL ONLY MAKE THEM SAD.

00:13.414 --> 00:15.216
WHAT?

00:15.216 --> 00:16.487
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

00:16.487 --> 00:18.789
HEY, GEORGE. HEY, ANGE.
 HEY, ERNIE.

00:18.789 --> 00:21.322
WHAT DO YOU GOT THERE?
 WHERE´S YOUR MOM?

00:21.322 --> 00:22.753
IT´S A FULL MOON,

00:22.753 --> 00:26.657
SO SHE´S PROBABLY OUT IN
 THE YARD COMBING HER FACE.

00:26.657 --> 00:28.729
GEORGE, GEORGE...

00:28.729 --> 00:31.162
I FOUND SOMETHING HERE
 YOU GOTTA SEE.

00:31.162 --> 00:34.265
I WAS AT WORK, MOVING THOSE
 OLD BOXES LIKE YOU ASKED,

00:34.265 --> 00:36.807
AND I CAME ACROSS
 YOUR MOM´S PERSONNEL FILE.

00:36.807 --> 00:38.769
YOU´RE NOT SUPPOSED
 TO LOOK AT THAT.

00:38.769 --> 00:40.211
THAT´S CONFIDENTIAL.

00:40.211 --> 00:43.074
YEAH, I KNOW,
 SO KEEP IT TO YOURSELF.

00:43.074 --> 00:45.416
IN 1965,

00:45.416 --> 00:48.749
SHE WAS WRITTEN UP FOR DATING
 THIS OTHER EMPLOYEE.

00:48.749 --> 00:50.321
HOW SHOULD I PUT THIS?

00:50.321 --> 00:52.453
SHE WAS FOUND
 IN THE BREAK ROOM

00:52.453 --> 00:56.087
WITH HER LANDING GEAR UP
 AND HER FLAPS DOWN.

00:56.087 --> 00:58.459
THIS COULDN´T HAVE
 HAPPENED IN 1965.

00:58.459 --> 01:01.292
I WAS BORN IN ´65.
 MY MOM WAS WITH MY DAD.

01:01.292 --> 01:04.235
SHE WAS ALSO SEEING
 THIS GUY LALO MONTENEGRO.

01:04.235 --> 01:07.638
I LOOKED UP HIS FILE, AND
 I GOT THIS PICTURE OF HIM.

01:07.638 --> 01:11.102
HUH. HE LOOKS
 KIND OF FAMILIAR.

01:11.102 --> 01:12.503
HE SHOULD.

01:12.503 --> 01:15.446
HE´S GOT GEORGE´S EYES,
 GEORGE´S HAIR,

01:15.446 --> 01:16.647
GEORGE´S NOSE.

01:16.647 --> 01:18.779
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING,
 ERNIE?

01:18.779 --> 01:21.452
THIS WRITE-UP WAS
 IN MARCH OF ´65.

01:21.452 --> 01:24.515
YOU WERE BORN NINE MONTHS
 LATER.

01:24.515 --> 01:26.517
MOM! MOM!

01:26.517 --> 01:27.718
WHAT?

01:27.718 --> 01:30.661
REMEMBER THIS GUY?

01:30.661 --> 01:34.595
LALO "THE PALO" MONTENEGRO.

01:34.595 --> 01:36.167
WHERE DID YOU GET THIS?

01:36.167 --> 01:38.499
AT WORK -- YOU WERE
 WRITTEN UP FOR DATING HIM

01:38.499 --> 01:40.831
AT THE SAME TIME
 YOU WERE WITH DAD.

01:40.831 --> 01:43.103
OH, FOR CRAP´S SAKE.

01:43.103 --> 01:45.276
LALO AND I WERE
 JUST GOOD FRIENDS.

01:45.276 --> 01:48.479
IT WAS RIGHT BEFORE MANNY AND I
 WERE GONNA GET MARRIED.

01:48.479 --> 01:51.542
WE WERE FIGHTING.
 I TURNED TO LALO FOR COMFORT.

01:51.542 --> 01:54.745
WE NEVER ONCE --

01:54.745 --> 01:56.647
OH.

01:56.647 --> 01:59.220
"OH," WHAT?!

01:59.220 --> 02:01.552
WELL, THERE WAS
 THIS ONE NIGHT.

02:01.552 --> 02:04.795
I GOT REAL MAD AT YOUR DAD
 FOR COMING HOME DRUNK.

02:04.795 --> 02:08.628
I GRABBED A BOTTLE OF TEQUILA
 AND RAN OVER TO LALO´S.

02:08.628 --> 02:12.633
AND THEN, UH, WE SORT OF
 SNUCK INTO THE FACTORY.

02:12.633 --> 02:16.767
WE ENDED UP FOOLING AROUND
 ON THE MANAGER´S DESK.

02:16.767 --> 02:19.510
I EAT OFF THAT DESK!

02:19.510 --> 02:23.143
AND THEN SOMEHOW WE ENDED UP
 IN THE BREAK ROOM,

02:23.143 --> 02:26.647
AND I REMEMBER WE WERE
 CRASHING INTO CHAIRS,

02:26.647 --> 02:28.319
ROLLING ON THE GROUND,

02:28.319 --> 02:31.652
AND THEN I WAS LIFTED UP
 ONTO SOMETHING.

02:31.652 --> 02:33.224
OKAY, MOM!

02:35.686 --> 02:37.658
DID YOU SLEEP WITH HIM?

02:37.658 --> 02:39.230
NO!

02:39.230 --> 02:40.791
I DON´T THINK SO!

02:40.791 --> 02:42.693
OH.

02:42.693 --> 02:44.265
I DON´T REMEMBER.

02:44.265 --> 02:47.698
IT WAS A BIG BOTTLE
 OF TEQUILA.

02:47.698 --> 02:49.370
WELL, I THINK YOU DID,

02:49.370 --> 02:52.543
´CAUSE THIS GUY´S GOT MY EYES,
 MY HAIR, AND MY NOSE!

02:52.543 --> 02:55.276
THIS IS CRAZY.
 MANNY´S YOUR DAD.

02:55.276 --> 02:56.547
YEAH?

02:56.547 --> 02:57.848
LET´S SEE THEN.

02:57.848 --> 02:59.950
YOU TELL ME.

02:59.950 --> 03:02.213
LALO? MANNY?

03:02.213 --> 03:04.415
MANNY? LALO?

03:04.415 --> 03:06.617
HUH.

03:06.617 --> 03:07.688
I´LL FIND LALO --

03:07.688 --> 03:09.260
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

03:09.260 --> 03:11.822
A MOTHER KNOWS THE FATHER
 OF HER OWN BABY.

03:11.822 --> 03:14.495
SO WHO IS IT THEN?

03:16.727 --> 03:19.430
ONE POTATO, TWO POTATO...

03:19.430 --> 03:21.872
OH...

03:24.575 --> 03:28.208
LOOK, MAN, THE SIGN SAYS,
 "NO SOLICITORS." LET´S GO.

03:28.208 --> 03:29.580
GEORGE, GEORGE...

03:29.580 --> 03:32.713
COME ON, MAN.
 THIS COULD BE YOUR DAD.

03:32.713 --> 03:34.715
AND YOU LOOK SO NICE.

03:34.715 --> 03:36.487
HE´S GONNA BE SO PROUD

03:36.487 --> 03:39.420
OF HIS HANDSOME,
 SUCCESSFUL BOY.

03:39.420 --> 03:42.623
[ Sobbing ] THE BOY
 HE NEVER KNEW.

03:42.623 --> 03:43.924
I CAN´T!

03:43.924 --> 03:45.596
THIS IS WHY ANGIE
 DIDN´T COME.

03:45.596 --> 03:49.330
SHE GETS ALL EMOTIONAL,
 AND SHE STARTS CRYING.

03:49.330 --> 03:50.831
HER T-SHIRT GETS WET.

03:50.831 --> 03:53.604
ANGIE SHOULD HAVE COME.

03:55.366 --> 03:56.507
YES?

03:56.507 --> 03:59.470
ARE YOU LALO MONTENEGRO?

03:59.470 --> 04:00.541
YEAH.

04:00.541 --> 04:02.513
DID YOU WORK AT
 POWERS AVIATION?

04:02.513 --> 04:04.315
YEAH, ABOUT 30 YEARS AGO.

04:04.315 --> 04:07.718
DO YOU REMEMBER A WOMAN
 NAMED BENITA LOPEZ?

04:07.718 --> 04:09.520
"BREAK ROOM" BENNY?

04:09.520 --> 04:12.423
OH.

04:12.423 --> 04:14.325
YEAH, I REMEMBER HER.

04:14.325 --> 04:15.756
WHAT´S THIS ALL ABOUT?

04:15.756 --> 04:17.728
WELL, I´M BENITA´S SON,
 GEORGE.

04:17.728 --> 04:19.930
AND THIS MAY COME
 AS A SHOCK TO YOU,

04:19.930 --> 04:22.393
BUT I THINK YOU COULD BE
 MY FATHER.

04:22.393 --> 04:23.864
WHAT DO WE HAVE HERE?

04:23.864 --> 04:27.568
OH, TWO STUDS...
 AND ME WITH NO HAMMER.

04:28.769 --> 04:30.601
LIKE YOU
 TO MEET CHARLES.

04:30.601 --> 04:34.274
I THINK THERE´S BEEN A MISTAKE.
 I WAS LOOKING FOR MY DAD.

04:34.274 --> 04:35.976
WELL, WE WERE LOOKING
 TO ADOPT,

04:35.976 --> 04:38.609
BUT WE WERE HOPING
 FOR SOMETHING SMALLER.

04:38.609 --> 04:41.612
LOOK,
 LET´S NOT STAND HERE.

04:41.612 --> 04:43.454
COME ON IN, PLEASE.

04:43.454 --> 04:46.286
I CAN´T BELIEVE
 YOU´RE BENNY´S SON.

04:46.286 --> 04:49.320
GOD, LOOK AT ALL THAT HAIR.
 I HATE YOU.

04:49.320 --> 04:52.363
HAVE A SEAT, EVERYONE.
 SIT DOWN.

04:52.363 --> 04:55.966
SO, WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
 I´M YOUR FATHER?

04:55.966 --> 04:58.469
WELL, AROUND THE TIME
 I WAS CONCEIVED,

04:58.469 --> 05:01.672
MY MOM WAS FIGHTING WITH
 THE GUY I THOUGHT WAS MY DAD,

05:01.672 --> 05:03.574
AND SHE SAID ONE NIGHT
 AFTER WORK

05:03.574 --> 05:06.607
YOU GUYS GOT TOGETHER
 AND, UH...YOU KNOW.

05:06.607 --> 05:08.539
SO...

05:08.539 --> 05:10.841
ERNIE GOT YOUR PICTURE
 FROM THE FILE,

05:10.841 --> 05:12.483
AND WE TRACKED YOU DOWN.

05:12.483 --> 05:13.744
[ LAUGHS ]

05:13.744 --> 05:16.347
SWEET BIRD OF YOUTH.

05:16.347 --> 05:19.390
I WAS BEAUTIFUL.
 I´D DO ME.

05:19.390 --> 05:21.892
[ LAUGHS ] [ LAUGHS ]

05:23.394 --> 05:26.757
SO, UH...
 DID YOUR MOTHER TELL YOU

05:26.757 --> 05:28.999
EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED
 THAT NIGHT?

05:28.999 --> 05:31.502
WELL, SHE SAID YOU GUYS
 WERE DRINKING

05:31.502 --> 05:33.864
AND THAT YOU LIFTED HER
 ONTO SOMETHING.

05:33.864 --> 05:35.666
BUT NOW I´M STARTING
 TO THINK

05:35.666 --> 05:38.369
MAYBE SHE LIFTED YOU
 ONTO SOMETHING.

05:42.513 --> 05:45.075
OH, MY. WE CAN´T POSSIBLY
 HAVE THIS DISCUSSION

05:45.075 --> 05:46.547
ON EMPTY STOMACHS.

05:46.547 --> 05:48.979
BRUSCHETTA, BRUSCHETTA,
 BRUSCHETTA?

05:52.022 --> 05:53.754
YOU´RE GOING
 TO TOO MUCH TROUBLE.

05:53.754 --> 05:55.486
OBVIOUSLY NOTHING HAPPENED.

05:55.486 --> 05:58.429
I´M JUST REACHING, ´CAUSE
 I´M TRYING TO FIND MY FATHER.

05:58.429 --> 06:00.060
I´M SORRY
 TO HAVE BOTHERED YOU.

06:00.060 --> 06:03.594
UH, COULD WE TAKE
 THE BRUSCHETTA TO GO?

06:03.594 --> 06:05.696
WHAT´S -- WHAT´S
 IN THE BOOK THERE?

06:05.696 --> 06:08.869
OH, MY WIFE MADE THIS
 IN CASE THIS WORKED OUT.

06:08.869 --> 06:10.541
IT´S A LITTLE PHOTO ALBUM.

06:10.541 --> 06:11.672
CAN I SEE IT?

06:11.672 --> 06:13.143
YEAH.

06:13.143 --> 06:14.745
THAT´S MY WIFE, ANGIE,

06:14.745 --> 06:17.077
AND THAT´S MY KIDS,
 CARMEN AND MAX.

06:17.077 --> 06:19.780
OH, GOD, THEY´RE ADORABLE.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

06:19.780 --> 06:22.052
WHAT´S THIS BIG EAR
 HERE?

06:22.052 --> 06:26.056
OH, THAT´S ME.
 MY HEAD DIDN´T FIT IN THE FRAME.

06:27.818 --> 06:30.891
YOU´RE A LUCKY MAN,
 GEORGE, YOU KNOW.

06:30.891 --> 06:33.464
I ALWAYS WANTED A FAMILY.

06:33.464 --> 06:36.066
IT´S TRUE. HE NEVER STOPS
 TALKING ABOUT IT.

06:36.066 --> 06:37.668
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

06:37.668 --> 06:40.871
YOU KNOW, I WASN´T AS DRUNK
 AS BENNY WAS THAT NIGHT.

06:40.871 --> 06:42.603
I DO REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED.

06:43.704 --> 06:46.507
YOU COULD DEFINITELY BE
 MY SON.

06:48.879 --> 06:50.441
ARE YOU OKAY?

06:50.441 --> 06:53.644
MAN, THIS IS A TRIP.
 I DON´T GET IT.

06:53.644 --> 06:54.445
I WAS YOUNG.

06:54.445 --> 06:55.946
I WAS CONFUSED.

06:55.946 --> 06:59.790
I DIDN´T KNOW WHETHER I LIKED
 MEN OR WOMEN AT THAT POINT,

06:59.790 --> 07:03.894
AND, WELL, BENNY SEEMED TO BE
 THE BEST OF BOTH WORLDS.

07:03.894 --> 07:05.125
YOU KNOW, I KNEW IT

07:05.125 --> 07:06.997
FROM THE MOMENT
 I SAW THE PICTURE.

07:06.997 --> 07:08.659
I KNEW IT WAS YOU.

07:08.659 --> 07:12.102
MAN, I´VE BEEN WANTING
 TO DO THIS MY WHOLE LIFE.

07:16.206 --> 07:19.169
THIS MUST BE A BIG MOMENT
 FOR YOU, TOO, HUH?

07:19.169 --> 07:21.912
HOW LONG HAVE YOU AND GEORGE
 BEEN TOGETHER?

07:21.912 --> 07:23.514
SINCE THE SECOND GRADE.

07:23.514 --> 07:26.076
IT´S ABOUT TIME YOU TOOK
 THE TRIP TO VERMONT

07:26.076 --> 07:27.748
AND MADE IT OFFICIAL.

07:27.748 --> 07:30.050
YEAH, OKAY.

07:30.050 --> 07:32.182
ROAD TRIP!

07:33.924 --> 07:37.087
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
 PLAYS ]

07:47.237 --> 07:53.043
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
 KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

08:23.133 --> 08:24.605
HEY, HOPE YOU´RE HUNGRY.

08:24.605 --> 08:26.837
I BROUGHT YOU SOME BRUSCHETTA.
 IT´S FABULOUS.

08:26.837 --> 08:28.909
I DON´T WANT TO HEAR
 ABOUT BRUSCHETTA.

08:28.909 --> 08:31.542
I WANT TO HEAR ABOUT LALO.
 DID YOU MEET HIM?

08:31.542 --> 08:34.885
YES, AND HE WAS WITH MY MOM,
 AND I THINK HE´S MY DAD,

08:34.885 --> 08:37.748
AND HIS LIFE PARTNER, CHARLES,
 MADE ME THIS BRUSCHETTA!

08:37.748 --> 08:39.149
ALL RIGHT, GO BACK.

08:39.149 --> 08:42.022
ANGIE, LALO´S INCREDIBLE.
 HE´S THIS GREAT GUY.

08:42.022 --> 08:44.193
HE´S SENSITIVE, HE´S GAY,
 HE WANTS ME,

08:44.193 --> 08:46.927
AND I´M SO HAPPY,
 I DON´T CARE HOW THAT SOUNDS.

08:46.927 --> 08:49.029
I HOPE IT´S OKAY --

08:49.029 --> 08:51.862
I INVITED LALO AND CHARLES OVER
 FOR THANKSGIVING.

08:51.862 --> 08:53.163
I´M SO HAPPY FOR YOU.

08:53.163 --> 08:55.205
I TOLD YOU YOUR MOM
 COULD TURN A MAN.

08:55.205 --> 08:56.667
YEAH.

08:56.667 --> 08:59.539
I GOTTA TELL THE KIDS
 I FOUND THEIR GRANDPA.

08:59.539 --> 09:01.171
CARMEN! MAX!
 GET DOWN HERE!

09:01.171 --> 09:04.645
YOU KNOW YOU HAVE TO EXPLAIN
 ABOUT CHARLES, TOO.

09:04.645 --> 09:06.046
OH. TAKE YOUR TIME, KIDS!

09:06.046 --> 09:07.648
WHAT´S UP?

09:07.648 --> 09:10.150
I GOT SOME GREAT NEWS
 AND SOME INTERESTING NEWS.

09:10.150 --> 09:12.152
I THINK
 I FOUND YOUR GRANDPA.

09:12.152 --> 09:13.784
REALLY?!

09:13.784 --> 09:16.556
I MIGHT HAVE EVEN FOUND
 YOU TWO GRANDPAS!

09:16.556 --> 09:18.929
WHAT?

09:18.929 --> 09:21.261
IT TURNS OUT THIS GUY,
 LALO MONTENEGRO,

09:21.261 --> 09:22.763
IS YOUR REAL GRANDFATHER,

09:22.763 --> 09:24.895
AND HE´S COMING OVER FOR
 THANKSGIVING

09:24.895 --> 09:26.837
WITH GRANDPA CHARLES,

09:26.837 --> 09:30.671
WHO WOULD NORMALLY BE...
 GRANDMA CHARLES.

09:30.671 --> 09:33.704
HE´S KIND OF LIKE
 A MAN GRANDMA --

09:33.704 --> 09:36.807
LIKE A...MAN-MA.

09:41.311 --> 09:42.653
OKAY, OKAY.

09:42.653 --> 09:45.315
WOW! MOM!
 ARE YOU A PARKING TICKET?

09:45.315 --> 09:49.189
´CAUSE YOU GOT "FINE, FINE,
 FINE!" WRITTEN ALL OVER YOU.

09:49.189 --> 09:51.291
HEY, COME ON,
 GET OFF MY BACK.

09:51.291 --> 09:52.823
IT´S JUST A DRESS.

09:52.823 --> 09:55.696
AND I HAVEN´T SEEN LALO
 OR HIS PALO IS A WHILE.

09:55.696 --> 09:57.597
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]
 I´LL GET IT.

09:57.597 --> 10:00.230
MOM, NO MATTER WHAT DRESS
 YOU´RE WEARING,

10:00.230 --> 10:02.973
I DON´T THINK LALO OR HIS PALO
 ARE GONNA NOTICE.

10:02.973 --> 10:04.234
HE FOUND HIS SOUL MATE.

10:04.234 --> 10:07.607
HI. I´M ANGIE.
 NICE TO MEET YOU.

10:07.607 --> 10:09.009
HI.

10:09.009 --> 10:11.011
I DON´T SEE
 ANY SOUL MATE.

10:11.011 --> 10:13.744
THE TALL GUY WITH
 THE STRONG CHIN?

10:13.744 --> 10:16.316
NICE TO MEET YOU.
 AND YOU MUST BE MAX.

10:16.316 --> 10:17.848
THAT´S MRS. MONTENEGRO.

10:17.848 --> 10:20.350
WHAT? NO WAY!

10:20.350 --> 10:21.922
[ LAUGHS ]

10:21.922 --> 10:24.895
CRAP! I PUT ON THESE
 CONTROL TOPS FOR NOTHING.

10:24.895 --> 10:26.626
WHY DIDN´T YOU TELL ME?

10:26.626 --> 10:29.359
´CAUSE I THOUGHT IT´D BE
 FUNNY -- LIKE IT IS.

10:29.359 --> 10:32.162
LALO, CHARLES,
 WELCOME TO OUR HOUSE.

10:32.162 --> 10:33.964
HEY, SON.
 HEY, DAD.

10:33.964 --> 10:36.006
HEY, CHARLES.
 HOW ARE YOU?

10:37.367 --> 10:39.309
BENITA?
 LALO.

10:39.309 --> 10:40.340
[ LAUGHS ]

10:40.340 --> 10:42.112
OH, GOD,
 LOOK AT YOU, GIRL.

10:42.112 --> 10:43.844
YOU HAVEN´T CHANGED A BIT.

10:43.844 --> 10:46.046
YOU HAVE.

10:47.317 --> 10:49.379
UH, I´D LIKE YOU
 TO MEET CHARLES.

10:49.379 --> 10:51.321
I´VE HEARD
 SO MUCH ABOUT YOU.

10:51.321 --> 10:53.784
I CAN´T BELIEVE
 WE´RE FINALLY MEETING.

10:53.784 --> 10:56.156
HOW YOU DOING?

10:57.427 --> 10:59.329
SHE´S SO BUTCH.

10:59.329 --> 11:00.991
HEY, GEORGE...

11:00.991 --> 11:03.794
WE HAVE SOMETHING
 FOR YOU.

11:03.794 --> 11:05.265
OH, THANKS, LALO.

11:05.265 --> 11:06.997
OH...

11:06.997 --> 11:10.670
"TO MY BABY BOY, GEORGE."

11:10.670 --> 11:14.044
IT´S THE LEAST WE COULD GET YOU.
 YOU GAVE US A FAMILY.

11:15.876 --> 11:17.247
[ Voice breaking ] DAMN...

11:17.247 --> 11:19.449
THERE´S A LOT OF SMOG
 IN THE VALLEY TODAY.

11:19.449 --> 11:20.680
LET´S EAT.

11:20.680 --> 11:21.952
THIS WAY, EVERYBODY.

11:21.952 --> 11:24.314
YOU DIDN´T EAT IT ALL
 ALREADY, DID YOU?

11:24.314 --> 11:25.415
OH, NO, I DIDN´T.

11:25.415 --> 11:26.686
GEORGE...

11:26.686 --> 11:27.888
I´LL BE OKAY, MOM.

11:27.888 --> 11:29.760
THAT´S GREAT.
 I DON´T CARE.

11:29.760 --> 11:32.823
LISTEN, IF HE´S A FLOWER,
 THEN WE DIDN´T DO IT.

11:32.823 --> 11:34.464
HE CAN´T BE YOUR DAD.

11:34.464 --> 11:37.197
NO, MOM, HE SAID YOU WERE
 THE LAST WOMAN

11:37.197 --> 11:40.100
HE WAS EVER WITH.

11:40.100 --> 11:44.034
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING.

11:44.034 --> 11:46.837
NO MAN BREAKS OFF
 A PIECE OF THIS

11:46.837 --> 11:49.709
AND THEN GIVES UP WOMEN.

11:51.441 --> 11:53.984
DID YOU SAY THAT TO HIM
 DURING SEX?

11:53.984 --> 11:56.146
´CAUSE THAT WOULD DO IT
 RIGHT THERE.

11:58.288 --> 12:01.351
HERE, LALO. YOU SIT
 AT THE HEAD OF THE TABLE.

12:01.351 --> 12:02.492
OH, OKAY.

12:02.492 --> 12:05.495
OKAY, BEFORE
 WE START EATING,

12:05.495 --> 12:06.897
LET´S SAY GRACE.

12:06.897 --> 12:08.959
I´LL DO IT THIS TIME.
 WHAT?

12:08.959 --> 12:10.260
SHUT UP.

12:12.903 --> 12:14.734
LORD, I WANT TO GIVE THANKS

12:14.734 --> 12:17.938
FOR ALL THE BLESSINGS
 YOU´VE GIVEN US --

12:17.938 --> 12:19.139
FOR ALL MY FAMILY,

12:19.139 --> 12:21.141
FOR EVERYONE´S HEALTH,

12:21.141 --> 12:23.443
BUT MOST OF ALL...FOR LALO.

12:23.443 --> 12:27.477
IF IT WASN´T FOR THIS MAN,
 I WOULDN´T BE HERE.

12:27.477 --> 12:31.481
I GUESS 19 HOURS OF WORKING
 THAT BIG HEAD THROUGH MY PELVIS

12:31.481 --> 12:33.083
DOESN´T MEAN JACK.

12:36.486 --> 12:39.489
AMEN.

12:39.489 --> 12:41.231
AMEN. AMEN.
 AMEN. AMEN.

12:44.394 --> 12:45.966
GEORGE...

12:45.966 --> 12:50.100
THAT WAS THE NICEST THING
 ANYBODY´S EVER SAID.

12:50.100 --> 12:52.973
OH, GOD, HERE COME
 THE WATERWORKS.

12:52.973 --> 12:56.206
EXCUSE ME.
 I´LL BE RIGHT BACK.

12:56.206 --> 12:57.447
UH, ANGIE...

12:57.447 --> 13:01.111
UH, YOU FORGOT
 THE CRANBERRY SAUCE.

13:10.891 --> 13:12.062
YOU ALL RIGHT?

13:12.062 --> 13:14.865
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
 I´LL BE OKAY.

13:14.865 --> 13:19.429
IT´S HARD TO BELIEVE IT´S
 BEEN 36 YEARS, HUH, LALO?

13:19.429 --> 13:21.031
I KNOW.

13:21.031 --> 13:24.104
THAT WAS A WILD NIGHT WE HAD,
 WASN´T IT?

13:24.104 --> 13:26.006
[ Laughing ] IT SURE WAS.

13:26.006 --> 13:28.208
YOU SURE WERE
 A GOOD KISSER.

13:28.208 --> 13:29.980
OH, AND SO WERE YOU.

13:29.980 --> 13:34.044
I MEAN, YOU ALMOST SUCKED
 A GOLD CAP OUT OF MY MOUTH.

13:34.044 --> 13:35.545
I STILL REMEMBER YOU

13:35.545 --> 13:39.049
TRACING THE OUTLINE
 OF THE BUTTERFLY TATTOO

13:39.049 --> 13:40.951
ON THE SMALL OF MY BACK.

13:40.951 --> 13:42.292
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:42.292 --> 13:44.154
HOW COULD I FORGET?

13:44.154 --> 13:47.227
A BUTTERFLY
 ON MY BUTTERCUP.

13:47.227 --> 13:49.359
DO I LOOK LIKE THE KIND
 OF WOMAN

13:49.359 --> 13:52.502
THAT WOULD HAVE A BUTTERFLY
 TATTOO ON HER BUTT?

13:52.502 --> 13:55.105
BLACK WIDOW?

13:55.105 --> 13:57.437
WE DIDN´T SLEEP TOGETHER,
 DID WE?

13:57.437 --> 14:00.040
DID WE?

14:00.040 --> 14:01.611
NO!

14:01.611 --> 14:03.843
YOU PASSED OUT.

14:03.843 --> 14:06.046
I HELD YOU ALL NIGHT LONG.

14:06.046 --> 14:09.179
WELL, I COULDN´T GET YOU
 OFF ME.

14:09.179 --> 14:11.481
I KNEW YOU WEREN´T
 GEORGE´S FATHER.

14:11.481 --> 14:16.056
BENNY, BENNY.
 DON´T -- DON´T SPOIL THIS.

14:16.056 --> 14:18.028
GEORGE ALWAYS WANTED
 A FATHER,

14:18.028 --> 14:19.990
AND I ALWAYS WANTED A SON.

14:19.990 --> 14:22.192
LOOK HOW HAPPY HE IS.

14:24.094 --> 14:26.997
DO YOU THINK HIS REAL FATHER
 COULD MAKE HIM

14:26.997 --> 14:29.239
ANY HAPPIER THAN HE IS
 RIGHT NOW?

14:41.351 --> 14:43.653
WELL, I HATE
 TO SPOIL THE PARTY,

14:43.653 --> 14:45.115
BUT WE HAVE TO GO.

14:45.115 --> 14:46.616
NO...
 NO...
 NO, DON´T GO.

14:46.616 --> 14:48.388
OH, DON´T WORRY.

14:48.388 --> 14:51.521
WE´LL SEE YOU ALL NEXT SATURDAY
 WHEN WE TAKE YOU FISHING.

14:51.521 --> 14:54.124
BUT BEFORE THAT,
 WE´RE GOING GO-KART RACING.

14:54.124 --> 14:55.465
ALL RIGHT!
 COOL!

14:55.465 --> 14:58.368
HE WAS TALKING TO ME.
 BACK OFF. YOU HAVE A DAD.

14:59.599 --> 15:02.402
THIS HAS BEEN A GREAT
 THANKSGIVING,

15:02.402 --> 15:05.575
AND IT SHOWS YOU
 WHAT´S REALLY IMPORTANT --

15:05.575 --> 15:07.337
FAMILY.

15:07.337 --> 15:09.339
FAMILY!

15:10.610 --> 15:12.943
I´LL WALK YOU GUYS
 TO THE CAR.

15:12.943 --> 15:15.415
NO, WE´LL DO IT.
 COME ON, GRANDPA.

15:15.415 --> 15:17.687
COME ON, MAN-MA.

15:22.392 --> 15:24.955
THIS HAS BEEN THE BEST
 THANKSGIVING EVER.

15:24.955 --> 15:27.357
AND WE MADE IT THROUGH
 THE WHOLE HOLIDAY

15:27.357 --> 15:28.458
WITH NO FIGHTING.

15:28.458 --> 15:31.361
WELL,
 IT´S NOT OVER YET.

15:31.361 --> 15:32.932
OH, HERE WE GO.

15:32.932 --> 15:35.365
LOOK, I GOT SOMETHING
 UNPLEASANT TO SAY,

15:35.365 --> 15:37.467
BUT I DON´T KNOW
 HOW TO SAY IT.

15:37.467 --> 15:39.439
DO IT LIKE
 YOU USUALLY DO --

15:39.439 --> 15:42.512
GET DRUNK AND CALL ME
 AT 3:00 IN THE MORNING.

15:42.512 --> 15:45.215
OKAY. HERE GOES.

15:45.215 --> 15:46.716
REMEMBER THOSE FAIRY TALES

15:46.716 --> 15:49.649
WHERE THE PRINCE WOULD COME
 AND SAVE THE PRINCESS

15:49.649 --> 15:52.282
AND THEY WOULD LIVE
 HAPPILY EVER AFTER,

15:52.282 --> 15:55.425
BUT ALL THAT CRAP DOESN´T
 REALLY HAPPEN IN REAL LIFE?

15:55.425 --> 15:57.687
WELL, LALO´S NOT YOUR DAD.

15:57.687 --> 16:00.530
WELL, WHY WOULD YOU
 SAY THAT, MOM?

16:00.530 --> 16:02.432
BECAUSE IT´S THE TRUTH.

16:02.432 --> 16:05.395
I´M TELLING YOU,
 I TALKED TO LALO.

16:05.395 --> 16:08.038
WE DIDN´T SPEND
 THE NIGHT TOGETHER.

16:08.038 --> 16:09.269
NOTHING HAPPENED.

16:09.269 --> 16:11.501
YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

16:11.501 --> 16:13.103
YOU´RE JEALOUS

16:13.103 --> 16:16.006
´CAUSE EVERYBODY LIKES LALO
 MORE THAN THEY LIKE YOU.

16:16.006 --> 16:18.978
WHEN ARE YOU GONNA
 FACE THIS, GEORGE?

16:18.978 --> 16:22.152
YOUR FATHER IS THAT BUM
 THAT RAN OUT ON US.

16:22.152 --> 16:25.555
GEORGE, IF YOU DON´T
 BELIEVE ME, ASK LALO.

16:25.555 --> 16:27.017
OUT.

16:27.017 --> 16:29.659
I WAS JUST GONNA MAKE
 A LITTLE PLATE --

16:29.659 --> 16:31.521
OUT!

16:31.521 --> 16:33.393
AND...

16:33.393 --> 16:36.366
NOW IT FEELS LIKE
 A HOLIDAY.

16:42.132 --> 16:44.404
THANKS FOR TAKING US
 FISHING, GRANDPA.

16:44.404 --> 16:46.106
HEY, THAT´S JUST
 THE BEGINNING.

16:46.106 --> 16:48.178
NEXT WEEK WE´RE GONNA SEE
 THE LAKERS,

16:48.178 --> 16:50.580
AND THE WEEKEND
 AFTER THAT -- DISNEYLAND.

16:50.580 --> 16:52.712
ALL RIGHT!
 HEY, MAYBE I CAN BRING SOMEONE.

16:52.712 --> 16:55.615
YOU GOT A GIRLFRIEND
 I DON´T KNOW ABOUT?

16:55.615 --> 16:58.017
NO WAY.
 GIRLS ARE GROSS.

16:59.219 --> 17:01.721
I SAID NOTHING.

17:01.721 --> 17:05.194
HE REALLY LIKES YOU,
 YOU KNOW.

17:05.194 --> 17:06.526
I LIKE HIM.

17:06.526 --> 17:09.459
I WISH I WAS AROUND
 TO SEE YOU AT THAT AGE.

17:09.459 --> 17:11.761
WE GOT A LOT
 OF CATCHING UP TO DO.

17:11.761 --> 17:14.733
HEY, CAN YOU CATCH ME UP
 ON ALLOWANCES?

17:14.733 --> 17:18.367
TOO LATE. I ALREADY SPENT IT
 ON BOTOX FOR CHARLES.

17:18.367 --> 17:22.712
YOU KNOW, I ALWAYS WANTED
 TO PLAY CATCH WITH MY DAD.

17:22.712 --> 17:25.345
LALO, ARE YOU REALLY
 MY DAD?

17:25.345 --> 17:28.248
WHY WOULD YOU ASK THAT?

17:28.248 --> 17:31.451
MY MOM TOLD ME NOTHING EVER
 HAPPENED BETWEEN YOU TWO.

17:31.451 --> 17:34.624
I WANT TO BELIEVE YOU, MAN,
 BUT I JUST GOTTA ASK.

17:34.624 --> 17:36.226
ARE YOU REALLY MY FATHER?

17:38.658 --> 17:41.761
WELL, IT DEPENDS ON
 HOW YOU DEFINE "FATHER."

17:41.761 --> 17:44.234
SOMEBODY WHO CARES
 ABOUT YOU?

17:44.234 --> 17:47.667
SOMEBODY WHO WANTS TO BE
 PART OF YOUR FAMILY?

17:47.667 --> 17:50.640
SOMEBODY WHO MADE OUT
 WITH YOUR MOM

17:50.640 --> 17:53.773
AND HAD TO PRETEND
 IT WAS SEAN CONNERY?

17:58.578 --> 18:00.680
NO, GEORGE,
 I´M NOT YOUR FATHER.

18:00.680 --> 18:04.314
THEN WHY WOULD YOU SAY
 YOU WERE?

18:04.314 --> 18:06.856
[ SIGHS ] BECAUSE
 I ALWAYS WANTED A CHILD,

18:06.856 --> 18:08.658
YOU KNOW, BUT BACK THEN,

18:08.658 --> 18:11.261
IT WASN´T AN OPTION
 FOR GUYS LIKE ME.

18:11.261 --> 18:12.722
AND THEN YOU SHOWED UP.

18:12.722 --> 18:15.695
AND YOU WERE EVERYTHING
 I EVER WANTED IN A SON.

18:15.695 --> 18:18.328
AND YOU HAD
 THAT PHOTO ALBUM

18:18.328 --> 18:21.601
WITH ALL THOSE ADORABLE
 PICTURES OF YOUR FAMILY

18:21.601 --> 18:25.335
AND THAT WEIRD PICTURE
 OF YOUR EAR.

18:25.335 --> 18:28.138
I COULDN´T RESIST.

18:28.138 --> 18:30.340
IT´S TOO BAD.

18:30.340 --> 18:32.842
YOU WOULD HAVE BEEN
 A GOOD DAD.

18:32.842 --> 18:35.715
I´M SORRY, GEORGE.

18:35.715 --> 18:40.820
YOU KNOW, THE KIDS DON´T HAVE
 ANY UNCLES.

18:40.820 --> 18:43.693
I´M TAKING APPLICATIONS.

18:43.693 --> 18:46.726
UNCLE LALO?

18:46.726 --> 18:48.898
AUNT CHARLES?

18:50.700 --> 18:52.662
I LIKE THE SOUND OF THAT.

18:52.662 --> 18:53.903
[ LAUGHS ]

18:53.903 --> 18:56.236
ARE YOU SURE
 WE´RE NOT RELATED?

18:56.236 --> 18:58.308
BECAUSE YOU THROW
 LIKE A GIRL.

18:58.308 --> 19:02.312
HEY, I DON´T NEED THAT,
 ESPECIALLY FROM A STRANGER.

19:02.312 --> 19:04.674
HEY, MAX, TAKE OVER
 FOR ME.

19:04.674 --> 19:05.915
SURE.

19:05.915 --> 19:08.848
I THINK I OWE SOMEBODY
 AN APOLOGY.

19:10.420 --> 19:12.752
SO, I GOT SOMETHING
 UNPLEASANT TO SAY,

19:12.752 --> 19:14.824
AND I DON´T KNOW
 HOW TO SAY IT.

19:14.824 --> 19:16.556
WELL, WHAT IS IT?

19:16.556 --> 19:18.858
REMEMBER
 IN THOSE FAIRY TALES

19:18.858 --> 19:22.192
WHEN SOMETIMES
 THE EVIL WITCH IS RIGHT

19:22.192 --> 19:24.334
AND THE HANDSOME PRINCE
 FINDS OUT

19:24.334 --> 19:26.866
THAT THE GAY GUY
 REALLY ISN´T HIS FATHER?

19:26.866 --> 19:29.869
DOES IT END WITH THE PRINCE
 GIVING THE WITCH

19:29.869 --> 19:31.401
THE REST OF THE TURKEY?

19:31.401 --> 19:32.642
YOU REALLY CAN´T BLAME ME.

19:32.642 --> 19:34.374
WHEN YOU LIE SO MUCH,

19:34.374 --> 19:37.207
IT´S HARD FOR ME TO TELL
 WHEN YOU´RE BEING HONEST.

19:37.207 --> 19:38.948
I ONLY LIE
 TO PROTECT YOU --

19:38.948 --> 19:40.880
OR WHEN IT´S CONVENIENT --

19:40.880 --> 19:43.753
OR, YOU KNOW, WHEN
 I´M JUST TOO DAMNED TIRED

19:43.753 --> 19:45.485
TO TELL YOU THE WHOLE TRUTH.

19:45.485 --> 19:49.889
WELL, I GUESS I GOTTA KEEP
 SEARCHING FOR MANNY LOPEZ.

19:49.889 --> 19:52.362
AT LEAST WE KNOW
 HE´S NOT GAY.

19:52.362 --> 19:55.295
THAT GUY...
 HE BROKE A PIECE OFF ME.

19:55.295 --> 19:58.698
AND HE CAME BACK FOR
 SECONDS AND THIRDS --

19:58.698 --> 20:00.930
OKAY, MOM!
 YOU CAN HAVE THE TURKEY!

20:00.930 --> 20:02.632
WHAT ABOUT THE BEER?

20:02.632 --> 20:03.903
DON´T PUSH YOUR LUCK.

20:03.903 --> 20:07.206
OH, YEAH, THAT MANNY,
 HE WAS AN ANIMAL.

20:07.206 --> 20:10.640
HE WAS THE ONLY MAN
 WHO COULD MAKE ME HOWL.

20:10.640 --> 20:11.941
OKAY, TAKE THE BEER.

20:11.941 --> 20:13.443
HEY, I GOT A STORY

20:13.443 --> 20:16.746
THAT´S GONNA MAKE YOU
 GIVE ME THE WHOLE HOUSE!

20:20.920 --> 20:23.393
YOU´RE A GUEST, AND
 YOU´RE ALWAYS CLEANING.

20:23.393 --> 20:27.257
IT´S WHAT I DO.
 CLEANING IS MY FOOTBALL.

20:27.257 --> 20:28.598
TOUCHDOWN.

20:28.598 --> 20:29.899
[ LAUGHS ]

20:29.899 --> 20:31.531
EXTRA POINT.

20:31.531 --> 20:33.363
EXTRA -- HUH?

20:33.363 --> 20:35.635
So, um...

20:35.635 --> 20:39.609
how long before I can tell him
 I´m not really your dad?

20:39.609 --> 20:50.450
Hey, wait till he finishes
 the living room.
